      <title>陷入困境的 Alecta 推迟盈利，等待财产股权估值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/alecta-postpones-earnings-to-get-fresh-figure-for-property-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典最大的养老基金 Alecta 推迟了全年业绩的公布，因为它正在等待其最大持股、负债累累的住宅业主 Heimstaden Bostad AB 的最新估值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/alecta-postpones-earnings-to-get-fresh-figure-for-property-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 14:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
